pages.text: The Jelly Rancher Strain$(br2)Base THC: 20% $(br)Base CBD: 5% $(br)Effect: Dolphin's Grace
Jelly Rancher Weed can be obtained by grinding your Fresh or Dried buds in a Grinder machine or using the manual grinder.
Jelly Rancher Seeds can be planted on farmland or inside the Grow Pot
Jelly Rancher Extract can be gained through the DNA Process or by extracting Jelly Rancher Weed in an Extractor
You can package your jelly rancher weed for easier distribution or selling to the stoner villager.
